    251          /*******************************************************************************
    252          * Function Name  : FLASH_GetFlagStatus
    253          * Description    : Checks the Flash flags.
    254          * Input          : None
    255          * Output         : None
    256          * Return         : The Flash flag errors.
    257          *                  The description of the Flash flag errors bits :
    258          *                      - Bit 0: Write error flag.
    259          *                      - Bit 1: Erase error flag.
    260          *                      - Bit 2: Program error flag.
