    311          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR1: Bank 0 sector 1.
    312          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR2: Bank 0 sector 2.
    313          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR3: Bank 0 sector 3.
    314          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR4: Bank 0 sector 4.
    315          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR5: Bank 0 sector 5.
    316          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR6: Bank 0 sector 6.
    317          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_SECTOR7: Bank 0 sector 7.
    318          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_MODULE:  Bank 0 module.
    319          *                      - FLASH_BANK1_SECTOR0: Bank 1 sector 0. (N.A for STR73x)
    320          *                      - FLASH_BANK1_SECTOR1: Bank 1 sector 1. (N.A for STR73x)
    321          *                      - FLASH_BANK1_MODULE:  Bank 1 module.   (N.A for STR73x)
