    374          *                      - FLASH_BANK0_MODULE:  Bank 0 module.
    375          *                      - FLASH_BANK1_SECTOR0: Bank 1 sector 0. (N.A for STR73x)
    376          *                      - FLASH_BANK1_SECTOR1: Bank 1 sector 1. (N.A for STR73x)
    377          *                      - FLASH_BANK1_MODULE:  Bank 1 module.   (N.A for STR73x)
    378          *                  - FLASH_NewState: Enable or disable the write protection.
    379          *                  This parameter can be one of the following values:
    380          *                      - ENABLE:  Enable the end of write interrupt.
    381          *                      - DISABLE: Disable the end of write interrupt.
    382          * Output         : None
